<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Reservation Confirmed</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f3f3f3;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #28a745;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h2>Reservation Confirmed 🎉</h2>
      <p>Dear <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Your reservation at our café has been <strong>approved</strong>!</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></li>
        <li><strong>Time:</strong> <%= time %></li>
        <li><strong>Reservation ID:</strong> <%= reservationID %></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We look forward to serving you. If you need any help, just reply to this
        email.
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        — Café XYZ<br />
        📍 Address: Main Street, Your City<br />
        ☎️ Phone: 123-456-7890<br />
        🌐 Website: www.cafexyz.com
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
